Class Event_Individual

  • java.lang.Object
    • pec.Event
      • event.Event_Simulation
        • event.Event_Individual
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<IEvent>, IEvent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Death, Move, Reproduction

    public abstract class Event_Individual
extends Event_Simulation
    Event_Individual is the abstract class that extends the Event abstract class and has the purpose of distinguish events that act on an individual (Move, Death and Reproduction) and events that act on the simulation it self (Observation).
    Author:
    Marta Marques (80882), Pedro Direita (81305), Jose Fernandes (82414)
